org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.opmode

Class AnnotatedOpModeClassFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.opmode.AnnotatedOpModeClassFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClassFilter

    public class AnnotatedOpModeClassFilter
extends java.lang.Object
implements ClassFilter
    Does the heavy lifting of managing annotation-based opmode registrations. This is modelled after the following, without which we could not have been successful in this endeavor. https://github.com/dmssargent/Xtensible-ftc_app/blob/master/FtcRobotController/src/main/java/com/qualcomm/ftcrobotcontroller/opmodes/FtcOpModeRegister.java Many thanks.
